        "ggGrDQ-Db-X_text": "<p>Back Pain Eased in Just Days</p>",
        "ggHHl0rr04p_text": "<p>4 Star</p>",
        "ggHO14NSlhZ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-727de96f-a9e8-4038-8526-7127e41159a7.png",
        "ggHP5SLxhc-_text": "<p>Price</p>",
        "ggHeaxzH-6T_text": "<p>I was really impressed when I started reading about the research behind these therapies.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Heat relaxes stiff muscles by improving blood flow, and massage helps reduce nerve pressure by loosening tension around the spine.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s the combination that makes the Triple Fusion Massager so effective at relieving sciatica and bringing back real mobility.</p>",
        "ggHpBHrYgbf_text": "<p><strong><u>Thermal Circulation Therapy</u></strong> uses heat to boost rehydration and bring healing nutrients to damaged spinal discs.</p>",
        "ggHpXq6PXJb_text": "<p>3,791 Ratings</p>",
        "ggIH6zlgDIe_text": "<p>Effectiveness</p>",
        "ggIkJyd9tJr_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-2a69d8ff-6f99-4b96-904f-adafa1525cd0.png",
        "ggJJtevaDcB_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8d759f93-dca8-483c-84a6-6fdfde7b1089.webp",
        "ggJRhNUU8zW_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8d759f93-dca8-483c-84a6-6fdfde7b1089.webp",
        "ggK03kTunUI_text": "<p>My daughter let me borrow hers, and I’ve been using it every day for just 15 minutes while lying down.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The results?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Truly life-changing.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>My lower back feels lighter, looser, and stronger.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I can sit without flinching, stand without bracing myself, and walk around the house without that stabbing nerve pain shooting down my leg.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>By the second day, I felt less stiff getting out of bed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Now, the pain that used to take over my mornings is almost completely gone.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Once the pressure between my vertebrae started to ease up, it felt like my spine could finally breathe again.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The discs had room to expand, the nerves weren’t being pinched anymore, and everything in my back just started working the way it’s supposed to.</strong></p>",
        "ggKNO-EIRnb_text": "It’s So Easy To Use",
        "ggKlnsPwwKS_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-880a17da-70f4-49ac-9175-1e3b4807227f.png",
        "ggLFGG4SSCQ_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/2588b58708ec41f99b77cf3c2b1e1f61.mp4",
        "ggLFGG4SSCQ_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggLFGG4SSCQ_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggLiV484GUn_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-1164e566-ab0c-4f09-be94-a9ef60ad5c76.png",
        "ggM1bzJDQI6_text": "<p>3,791 customer ratings</p>",
        "ggMLBTdkwz7_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/9e2fd1f201bb4d21a5ca86ab77b72611.mp4",
        "ggMLBTdkwz7_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggMLBTdkwz7_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggNIO8yB_Ji_text": "The Science Behind SmoothSpine",
        "ggNRnMhFRrr_text": "<p>Reviewed in the United States on April 17, 2025</p>",
        "ggOvbT9qrRm_text": "<p>Now, after using the Triple Fusion Massager:</p>",
        "ggPmjKywctB_text": "<p>I stand, bend, and stretch without fear or hesitation</p>",
        "ggPyzZ8BbZh_text": "<p>I’ve returned to my hobbies and even joined a walking group</p>",
        "ggQYCKaj2iT_text": "<p>Karen Mitchell</p>",
        "ggQhR1IpVck_text": "My Experience Using SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Massager",
        "ggQmZ-m-ifM_text": "<p>I couldn’t sit through a meal without shooting pain down my leg</p>",
        "ggQsB0hj91f_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/d1ff3458a11546a0b0717ed829d0cea4.mp4",
        "ggQsB0hj91f_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggQsB0hj91f_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggSag6O2AwP_text": "<p>If the space between your spinal discs isn’t restored, <strong>your vertebrae will keep collapsing</strong>, trapping the nerves that run through your back and legs.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The pressure builds, pinching those nerves tighter, and triggering the burning, stabbing, or numbing pain that <strong>makes walking, sitting, or even lying down unbearable.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Over time, your spine stiffens, your mobility fades, and the pain becomes more constant, setting off a cycle where even simple movements start to feel impossible.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I was terrified of where this was heading.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Would I lose the ability to move without help?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Would I become stuck at home, watching life pass me by from a recliner?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>But thankfully, there was hope…</strong></p>",
        "ggT6Xm4BV4u_text": "If You Don’t Restore Your Disc Height, The Pain Will Only Get Worse",
        "ggTrfq6UZe5_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-312b5de8-f238-4bba-b3f4-dd057015f45b.png",
        "ggUCruVTMuv_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4ee35975-73ca-4d69-ab20-3d81af37d4da.png",
        "ggUPrKz2la5_text": "<p>I used to deal with constant pain, stiffness, and nerve flare-ups in my lower back. But after using the Triple Fusion Massager, I can finally say I feel like myself again. No burning, no locking up, and no fear of movement.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The difference is night and day.</p>",
        "ggVSENpLP98_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8ecaa635-3714-4e8e-9906-8479b4b3e2c9.png",
        "ggWbvzXc-Rp_text": "<p>90%</p>",
        "ggWxFBklBXM_text": "<p>Comfort</p>",
        "ggX4W7xuCgc_label": "<p>GET 60% OFF<br>SmoothSpine NOW!</p>",
        "ggYqXKhd5XU_text": "<p>\"I’ve dealt with chronic back tension for years, and the <span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(34,35,35);font-size:17px;\">SmoothSpine</span> was the first product that gave me noticeable relief. Just a few sessions in, I felt my spine decompress and my posture improve. The tightness in my lower back started to melt away. It’s been a true breakthrough for my daily comfort and mobility!\"</p>",
        "ggZFFQLQgn9_text": "<p>1%</p>",
        "ggZUgK4E852_text": "Limited Time Offer: 60% Off SmoothSpine",
        "ggZZkMDXkBo_text": "<p>Linda Chapman</p>",
        "ggZrxLRh85C_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-57507250-c0b0-43ed-a9b3-5bdef2a6c33a.png",
        "gg_ve15hqdq_text": "<p><strong><u>TargetPoint Massage Therapy</u></strong> has micro-vibration nodes that mimic the hands of a massage therapist, targeting deep knots and tight muscles to release tension, ease stiffness, and promote circulation for faster results.</p>",
        "ggbCmxvWeJz_text": "<p>I can sit comfortably for hours, no more nerve flare-ups</p>",
        "ggc9AgGhBaX_text": "<p>Home &gt; Pain Relief &gt; Sciatica</p>",
        "ggcu5kkA4Cb_text": "<p>All the controls are built right into the top of the device.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Just tap the buttons to choose if you want to go through the automatic program, or manually choose 1 of the 3 therapy styles.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I always start with a setting that feels comfortable, then gradually increase it as my body loosens up, <strong>letting the combination of gentle stretch, targeted massage, and soothing heat take over.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The traction creates space in my spine, and the massage seems to wake up the muscles around it, getting blood flowing and helping everything move the way it should.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Even with just the massage alone, it feels incredible, but once the heat kicks in, it’s like all the stiffness and pressure just melts away. That’s when I really feel the difference.</p>",
        "ggddIsF_Yrb_text": "<p>If you're dealing with chronic back pain, sciatica, or stiffness, I truly recommend trying the Triple Fusion Massager.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>It’s helped me more than I ever expected, and I honestly believe it could make a real difference for you too.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Now, I know what you might be thinking - what does something like this cost?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I had that same concern in the beginning.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But after feeling the kind of relief I’ve had, I can honestly say that it’s worth every penny.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The regular price for a Triple Fusion Massager is $274.95.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And for the quality of the therapy, the technology built into it, and the long-term results, <strong>that’s already an incredible deal.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I’ve spent far more on things that did nothing but cover up the pain for a few hours.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But here’s the exciting news…</p>",
        "ggdeViqKQt6_text": "The Solution That Changed My Life",
        "ggdq-TQlJNi_text": "Customer Reviews",
        "gge6vAxXpHV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-312b5de8-f238-4bba-b3f4-dd057015f45b.png",
        "ggeM4ZPFrQK_text": "<p>I was afraid to travel because long car rides left me in agony</p>",
        "gges87UOu7Y_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-476670ba-a8fe-4b3a-a431-f3339147051c.png",
        "ggesFPW7uhF_text": "<p>Quality</p>",
        "ggfNKHA0lZC_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-65419afd-ec3c-41e2-87d6-655eedd8c34d.webp",
        "ggfsHUyceMR_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-57507250-c0b0-43ed-a9b3-5bdef2a6c33a.png",
        "gggGNSQX-9r_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/c16a82718c5b492ebb40d0f70a9f95a1.mp4",
        "gggGNSQX-9r_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gggGNSQX-9r_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gghIEzubHV__srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-57507250-c0b0-43ed-a9b3-5bdef2a6c33a.png",
        "gghdUbBA9t7_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-7f8ec3e6-1a39-4ee6-b91c-fb705c8067b0.png",
        "ggiQNatiN8L_text": "<p>7%</p>",
        "ggin4XGvIX4_text": "<p>William Burke</p>",
        "ggj5656jpKw_text": "<p>I feel confident planning trips again and getting out of the house</p>",
        "ggjq0bpAws4_text": "<p>After seeing how much I was struggling, my daughter told me about a strange back therapy she’d been doing at home…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It came after her doctor told her the real reason for her sciatica…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And how most people are focusing on the wrong thing when trying to relieve sciatica and back pain…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>It turns out the real problem with sciatica <u>all starts with the spinal discs…</u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You see, those discs are supposed to act like shock absorbers - keeping space between your vertebrae and protecting the nerves that run through your spine.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But as we age, those discs start to shrink, forcing your vertebrae closer together, pushing the discs out of place, and compressing the nerves</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Like a mattress that’s been slept on for too many years, they flatten out and stop supporting the structure above them.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Discs getting pushed out of place pinch the nerves, causing that burning, stabbing, or numbing pain in your back, hips, and legs.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That’s why none of the solutions I tried ever worked.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They were all focused on the symptoms, but they did nothing to relieve the compression or restore the spinal discs where the real problem was hiding.</p>",
        "ggjzEHuFPgy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-85bac3d6-1bfa-468d-90d9-aa156b9f960c.jpg",
        "ggk50N3Vywd_text": "<p>Hi, I'm Evelyn, and I want to share my journey with sciatica and relentless back pain, and how I finally found relief.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For months, I was dealing with a constant ache in my lower back that turned into sharp, burning pain shooting down my leg.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Simple things like standing at the sink or walking to the mailbox became exhausting.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sciatica pain was stealing the life I used to enjoy.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I tried everything - posture braces, stretching routines, heat pads, even painkillers my doctor prescribed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But nothing gave me lasting relief.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Each morning I woke up <strong>feeling more helpless and more afraid</strong> that this was just how the rest of my life would feel.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Keep reading, because I did find a solution - and I’m going to share it with you in just a moment…</p>",
        "ggkgu5nue7f_text": "<p>5.0</p>",
        "gglPNimzCf1_text": "<p>I'm incredibly thankful to be on the road to recovery now by simply using SmoothSpine for 5 to 15 minutes per day from the comfort of my own home.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>I'm basically reversing what caused the issue in the first place, which is the thin collapsing discs in my spine.</strong></p>",
        "gglbwd1ZED9_text": "<p><strong><u>Dynamic Traction Therapy</u> </strong>gently stretches and separates your vertebrae, reducing pressure on pinched nerves and allowing your spinal discs to rehydrate and regain their natural cushioning.</p>",
        "ggmYAZDN3lo_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-5bf8297a-9c56-4d2d-bc80-2f1c2ef7f9c7.png",
        "ggmpFJeXwnz_text": "<p>Verified Purchase</p>",
        "ggn-CGnN_Bf_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b7aa7053-3454-498a-beb4-449144decbc9.png",
        "ggn0Kiy3vDa_text": "How SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Massager Works",
        "ggnCnEAn8Ju_text": "<p>1 Star</p>",
        "ggoSoJ7cK28_text": "Your Chance To Experience Relief",
        "ggpJmQACl5n_text": "By Feature",
        "ggrFA2-2oOZ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-312b5de8-f238-4bba-b3f4-dd057015f45b.png",
        "ggrMq7oQsyw_text": "What Others Are Saying About SmoothSpine",
        "ggrRiHRQGEG_text": "<p>5 Star</p>",
        "ggrjSqzlPGy_text": "My Transformation: From Feeling Fragile and Afraid to Standing Tall and Living Again",
        "ggrzy2IJNlU_text": "<p>5.0</p>",
        "ggtIiDhFwSw_text": "<p>\"After years of poor circulation in my legs, I was constantly dealing with swelling and pain. I finally tried SmoothSpine, and the difference is unbelievable. It's simple to use and incredibly effective—my legs feel light, pain-free, and finally back to normal!\"</p>",
        "ggtKkWj920i_text": "My Sciatica Was So Bad I Couldn’t Stand, Sit, or Sleep Without Feeling Like My Spine Was on Fire…",
        "ggtSsFZJaHa_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-312b5de8-f238-4bba-b3f4-dd057015f45b.png",
        "ggtZSSr4Djc_text": "<p>I never thought I’d be telling strangers what it felt like to crawl across the floor - but you need to understand just how bad my back pain had become.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Some mornings, I couldn’t even stand upright.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>My spine felt like it was collapsing in on itself, and <strong>the pain shooting down my legs was so intense I’d break out</strong> in a cold sweat just trying to move.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Even my daughter looked at me one morning and said, “Mom… this isn’t normal.”</p>",
        "ggtzUrjZrcz_text": "<p>These are just a few of the 4,000+ 5-star reviews the Triple Fusion Massager has received. It's helping people of all ages finally move freely, sleep better, and take their lives back from back pain.</p>",
        "ggu4Jq_I7EJ_text": "<p>Verified Purchase</p>",
        "ggvfzP7Hf1I_text": "<p>The \"Triple Fusion\" massager uses three therapies to solve this right at the source:</p>",
        "ggwEKdkM7Xr_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/e0112b6395d7442c888c6684ad97b735.mp4",
        "ggwEKdkM7Xr_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggwEKdkM7Xr_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggwjRJ8CPUO_text": "<p>4.8 out of 5</p>",
        "ggwlVhxu7Yb_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-87ec105b-8e30-49a7-80b3-f68a6fc5c9f0.webp",
        "ggxRn6ILnfg_text": "<p>2 Star</p>",
        "ggy4YXIPYCG_text": "<p>Standing for more than a few minutes left my lower back throbbing</p>",
        "ggyOm7qn9eJ_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/9c98f123e4a64a8bb8cea9b8d220bb81.mp4",
        "ggyOm7qn9eJ_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggyOm7qn9eJ_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggyPwWEeEo__srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4ee35975-73ca-4d69-ab20-3d81af37d4da.png",
        "ggyt_6ciwbo_text": "<p>I started with just a 5 minute session and slowly increased the length every few days as my body got used to it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It felt good knowing I could adjust everything—because every back is different, and having that kind of control made it feel safer and more effective.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>What matters most to me is that the Triple Fusion Massager doesn’t just numb the pain like pills or patches, it actually treats what’s causing it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You just lie down, press a button, and it’s like getting a full spinal therapy session without ever leaving your house.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>It’s simple to use, and surprisingly quiet too.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I usually use it while resting in bed or watching my shows in the evening, and it never interrupts anything.</p>",
        "ggzMBALwSDK_text": "<p>4.8</p>"
